SAMSON Materials Handling has appointed Mr Dale Lockley as the new sole managing director. SAMSON Materials Handling is part of the internationally renowned AUMUND Group of Companies, which specialises in professional bulk handling solutions and products that provide the very highest levels of performance and engineering. Dale Lockley has over 20 years of experience working within and leading international multidisciplinary teams and developing materials handling technologies of worldwide operating companies including more than seven years as managing director. He initially joined SAMSON in 2016 as senior project manager and later worked as programme delivery manager. As a qualified mechanical engineer, as well as an experienced businessman, Dale Lockley brings an important combination of technical and commercial knowledge to SAMSON Materials Handling. He is pleased to be working with the AUMUND Group and is keen to maximise internal synergies and strengthen external relationships in order to provide the best possible bulk materials handling systems to customers worldwide.